 247:../Middlewares/threadx/ports/cortex_m55/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** /* Determine whether or not stack checking is enabled. By default, ThreadX stack checking is
 248:../Middlewares/threadx/ports/cortex_m55/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    disabled. When the following is defined, ThreadX thread stack checking is enabled.  If stack
